 enables more accurate investigations on\nthe galaxy-halo connection and other important related issues, including\ngalactic conformity and the effect of halo assembly bias on galaxy assembly.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jul 2019 18:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 5 Aug 2019 00:59:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-21"}
