e corrected state annotations. We are publicly releasing\nMultiWOZ 2.1 to the community, hoping that this dataset resource will allow for\nmore effective models across various dialogue subproblems to be built in the\nfuture.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 2 Jul 2019 22:30:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 20 Nov 2019 21:06:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 22 Nov 2019 18:34:38 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 3 Dec 2019 22:41:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-05"}
